(1, 1, '2014-04-23 22:37:35', '2014-04-23 22:37:35', 'Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging!', 'Hello world!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hello-world', '', '', '2014-04-23 22:37:35', '2014-04-23 22:37:35', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/SD-nonprofits/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(2, 1, '2014-04-23 22:37:35', '2014-04-23 22:37:35', 'This is an example page. It''s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I''m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin'' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="http://localhost:8888/SD-nonprofits/wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!', 'Sample Page', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sample-page', '', '', '2014-04-23 22:37:35', '2014-04-23 22:37:35', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/SD-nonprofits/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(3, 1, '2014-04-23 22:38:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 'Auto Draft', '', 'auto-draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2014-04-23 22:38:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/SD-nonprofits/?p=3', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4, 1, '2014-04-23 22:39:17', '2014-04-23 22:39:17', '<p>Your Name (required)<br />\n    [text* your-name] </p>\n\n<p>Your Email (required)<br />\n    [email* your-email] </p>\n\n<p>Subject<br />\n    [text your-subject] </p>\n\n<p>Your Message<br />\n    [textarea your-message] </p>\n\n<p>[submit "Send"]</p>\n[your-subject]\n[your-name] <[your-email]>\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n--\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on San Diego Non Profits (http://localhost:8888/SD-nonprofits)\neleija.creates@gmail.com\n\n\n0\n\n[your-subject]\n[your-name] <[your-email]>\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n--\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on San Diego Non Profits (http://localhost:8888/SD-nonprofits)\n[your-email]\n\n\n0\nYour message was sent successfully. Thanks.\nFailed to send your message. Please try later or contact the administrator by another method.\nValidation errors occurred. Please confirm the fields and submit it again.\nFailed to send your message. Please try later or contact the administrator by another method.\nPlease accept the terms to proceed.\nPlease fill the required field.', 'Contact form 1', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'contact-form-1', '', '', '2014-04-23 22:39:17', '2014-04-23 22:39:17', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/SD-nonprofits/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&p=4', 0, 'wpcf7_contact_form', '', 0),
(6, 1, '2014-02-24 15:52:55', '2014-02-24 15:52:55', 'Nullam augue cupidatat litora phasellus blandit integer tellus libero facere architecto, egestas? Morbi sem voluptates eu, cursus. Deserunt repellat aliquip, deleniti! Occaecat. Nullam turpis, adipiscing vitae fugit placerat, blandit deleniti, ipsum mauris fusce massa feugiat?\n\nExercitationem? Tenetur hac cupiditate lacus? Ipsam repudiandae fugit pede aliquip curae corporis iste? Eleifend. Doloremque, dolorem porta, sequi blanditiis? Elementum minim ridiculus ac nostra laborum, aut ante pellentesque?\n\n<!--more-->\n\nRatione nibh integer, ut nunc. Repudiandae sem, aperiam hac! Fringilla sociis minima? Sollicitudin aliquam dicta fugiat irure molestiae litora consequatur mauris. Necessitatibus officia penatibus debitis porttitor exercitation? Provident sint nec consectetur cras venenatis quo quod cillum placeat.\n\nFeugiat aliquam quas condimentum dolores explicabo nostrud lectus nostra a, dolorem vestibulum eget cillum necessitatibus. Sequi orci ullamcorper? Sociis? Mus, sunt quaerat aliquet orci. Nemo montes, viverra tempora maiores voluptates aenean eros hymenaeos semper sociis officiis, praesent class mus mus. Scelerisque praesent, ducimus porttitor auctor curabitur, fugit cupiditate, tristique suscipit excepteur optio! Amet porta, occaecati beatae pretium proin possimus provident sodales facilisi impedit explicabo voluptatum ligula per eleifend, iusto delectus? .\n\nSuscipit. Adipiscing, pariatur, ultrices interdum tellus unde libero! Viverra etiam. Asperiores commodo, nihil, eum magnis vulputate. Modi sunt facilisi exercitation, numquam excepturi! Eu convallis unde imperdiet, torquent laborum! Ultricies itaque corrupti cillum rhoncus nihil nisi donec praesentium pellentesque! Cras voluptas scelerisque eiusmod! Parturient dictumst varius porro morbi taciti massa placeat a temporibus fugiat nemo? Eius adipisci recusandae fuga molestias iure.', 'Our Urban Development Plan', '\nElementum in cupidatat blanditiis, morbi similique ratione cubilia voluptate, esse, autem cillum magni perspiciatis, augue ullam, elementum lectus magnis, morbi.\n\nEligendi autem porro mauris, minus laoreet lacus incididunt sequi inceptos phasellus illo? Atque dolores ipsa, voluptates nihil nobis iusto, magnam nostrum mi eget tempor.\n', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'standard-post-format', '', '', '2014-02-24 15:52:55', '2014-02-24 15:52:55', '', 0, 'http://rescuethemes.com/themes/advocator/?p=6', 0, 'post', '', 5),
(9, 1, '2014-02-24 16:13:41', '2014-02-24 16:13:41', 'How do I love thee? Let me count the ways (in 140 characters or less).', 'Status Post Format', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'status-post-format', '', '', '2014-02-24 16:13:41', '2014-02-24 16:13:41', '', 0, 'http://rescuethemes.com/themes/advocator/?p=9', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(13, 1, '2014-02-23 16:16:51', '2014-02-23 16:16:51', '<blockquote>"Never be afraid to raise your voice for honesty and truth and compassion against injustice and lying and greed."\n<cite><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_Faulkner">William Faulkner</a></cite></blockquote>', 'Quote Post Format', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'quote-post-format', '', '', '2014-02-23 16:16:51', '2014-02-23 16:16:51', '', 0, 'http://rescuethemes.com/themes/advocator/?p=13', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(16, 1, '2014-02-21 16:25:23', '2014-02-21 16:25:23', '<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Movements_for_civil_rights" title="Movements for civil rights">The Civil Rights Movement.</a>', 'Link Post Format', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'link-post-format', '', '', '2014-02-21 16:25:23', '2014-02-21 16:25:23', '', 0, 'http://rescuethemes.com/themes/advocator/?p=16', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(19, 1, '2014-02-22 16:30:59', '2014-02-22 16:30:59', 'Q: "Do you know how many records you''ve sold up to the present time?"\n\nRINGO: "Uhh, well... The last count was, umm, six million, I think.\n\nJOHN: (jokingly) "That''s just Ringo''s records."\n\nPAUL: (laughs)\n\nRINGO: "Well, the others'' are on sale."', 'Chat Post Format', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'chat-post-format', '', '', '2014-02-22 16:30:59', '2014-02-22 16:30:59', '', 0, 'http://rescuethemes.com/themes/advocator/?p=19', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(21, 1, '2014-02-20 16:32:56', '2014-02-20 16:32:56', 'This is an aside post format. I never tried to prove nothing, just wanted to give a good show. My life has always been my music, it''s always come first, but the music ain''t worth nothing if you can''t lay it on the public. The main thing is to live for that audience, ''cause what you''re there for is to please the people.', 'Aside Post Format', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'aside-post-format', '', '', '2014-02-20 16:32:56', '2014-02-20 16:32:56', '', 0, 'http://rescuethemes.com/themes/advocator/?p=21', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(24, 1, '2014-02-18 16:34:40', '2014-02-18 16:34:40', 'Quos elementum earum, conubia praesentium quos? Cursus blandit saepe, elit nonummy, volutpat magnam numquam, euismod sagittis qui ea, tempora commodi repellat porttitor?\n\nItaque proident scelerisque tempore sunt, odio lobortis maecenas, dolore mattis! Non velit, occaecati adipisci omnis recusandae dolorum, reiciendis, hendrerit accusamus!\n\n<!--more-->\n\nCupiditate diamlorem culpa quae alias magnam ullamco nam, ab porro. Perspiciatis perspiciatis nostrud accusamus eiusmod totam magnis quibusdam eleifend gravida.\n\nMagni nascetur ex placeat unde laboriosam litora feugiat omnis sapiente eleifend mauris, inceptos eveniet torquent ullamcorper. Velit, accusamus inceptos feugiat magni nobis asperiores pede, mi metus vehicula eu dictumst voluptate eos. Facilisi. Morbi amet netus illum blanditiis, commodo venenatis, earum, maecenas non senectus voluptas quo tempore? Ac recusandae voluptatibus adipiscing ornare exercitation vivamus recusandae. \n\nBlandit sapien consectetur? Non natus dolorem, nihil eros facilis, perferendis nascetur, molestias quo diamlorem etiam assumenda, proident accumsan, justo, fuga tempore cubilia! Provident, aut quos eum, error? Dolore placeat? Gravida? Aliqua consectetuer! Porro congue qui facilis. Magni convallis tristique fugit error iure! Interdum sint, at convallis.\n', 'Standard Post Form Without a Featured Image', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'standard-post-form-without-featured-image', '', '', '2014-02-18 16:34:40', '2014-02-18 16:34:40', '', 0, 'http://rescuethemes.com/themes/advocator/?p=24', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(32, 1, '2014-02-23 16:43:55', '2014-02-23 16:43:55', 'Illo. Ultricies habitasse, nisl officiis sociosqu, impedit nostrud praesent, pulvinar laudantium aenean! Sollicitudin penatibus suscipit, placerat magna, mattis! Accusamus, dolorem iusto? Eos eget vero vestibulum ullam tenetur, rem consequat maecenas eaque integer pretium, commodo nostrum? Montes lobortis turpis mattis! Assumenda, ante placerat!\n\n<!--more-->\n\nQuisquam accusamus cillum voluptatum doloribus condimentum eveniet? Per. Montes consequat laborum pharetra interdum qui officia, natoque, velit nunc, dolorem illum rutrum iaculis? Fugit nihil, quis ad congue eaque, consequatur pulvinar commodi voluptatum pellentesque laoreet, tenetur faucibus? Senectus, culpa? Amet etiam? Mi ab? Soluta, magnis iusto nec, quasi deserunt gravida eu similique maiores consequat, officia litora ac metus excepteur.\n\nSunt maxime hymenaeos facilisis pretium? Congue vero augue, iusto delectus, ridiculus sodales! Sed? Litora irure? Ligula parturient? Dictumst, suspendisse occaecat! Unde blandit nostrum nisi nam inceptos? Dictumst quia magnis penatibus, explicabo, primis officia purus maecenas nostrum? Architecto porro, sollicitudin incidunt!\n\nPariatur facilisis iure netus magni hac exercitation nesciunt nesciunt quae tellus habitasse praesentium proident amet viverra! Arcu ridiculus! Cupidatat? Excepteur? Sapiente tenetur, tempor nibh, dis nostrum optio lacus autem habitant? Porta malesuada, repudiandae tortor, corporis, fringilla rhoncus numquam, doloribus incidunt, occaecat, interdum? Rhoncus dictumst tincidunt cras illo porttitor! Nemo magni. Tempus ornare reprehenderit viverra commodi, massa habitasse repudiandae molestias perferendis.', 'Another Standard Post Format', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'another-standard-post-format', '', '', '2014-02-23 16:43:55', '2014-02-23 16:43:55', '', 0, 'http://rescuethemes.com/themes/advocator/?p=32', 0, 'post', '', 0),
